Climatology Plugin for OpenCPN
==============================

climatology plugin for opencpn

Compiling
=========

* git clone git://github.com/seandepagnier/climatology_pi.git

Under windows, you must find the file "opencpn.lib" (Visual Studio) or "libopencpn.dll.a" (mingw) which is built in the build directory after compiling opencpn.  This file must be copied to the plugin directory.

Build as normally:

* cd ..
* cd build
* cmake ..
* make
* make install

Please note the plugin requires about 5-7mb of data. If the data is missing from the package, it can be found at 
http://sourceforge.net/projects/opencpnplugins/files/climatology_pi/    CL-DATA-1.0.tar.xz
Please unpack into plugins/climatology_pi/data directory.

